summary: AN ORDINANCE amending Plat 37W, Page 104 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, to rezone certain property extending 75 feet north of a point 160 feet north of East Thomas Street between Coryell Court East and 19th Avenue East from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM 800) Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith (Petition of Seattle Housing Authority, C.F. 289046).
